title: JAN 11 2022 - W.H.O. SELECTED CASS SUNSTEIN TO HEAD COVID PSYCHOLOGICAL RESPONSE UNIT
description:
The World Health Organization selected Cass Sunstein to head its COVID Response Psychological Unit, a hemorrhagic fever breaks out in Northwest China weeks before Olympics to start, CNN producer John Griffin slapped with $15M civil suit for child sex exploitation, and the Kazakhstan intelligence chief, who was Hunter Biden's 'close friend', was arrested for treason.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
